data.description: Welcome to a realm of unparalleled luxury and sophistication! This exceptional residence, boasting 6 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, is a harmonious blend of historic charm and modern amenities, creating a living experience that transcends expectations. As you step into this architectural masterpiece, a new elevator awaits to seamlessly transport you across all three floors, ensuring accessibility and convenience. The property is encased in a fortress-like brick wall, providing both security and an air of grandeur reminiscent of a bygone era. The garage, equipped with a mini-split system, is not just a space for your vehicles but a temperature-controlled haven for your belongings.Inside, exquisite historic-like details adorn every corner, creating an atmosphere of timeless elegance. Twonew water heaters guarantee an ample supply of hot water, while the brand new roof with a warranty and cutting-edge new HVAC systems ensure a worry-free living experience. The heart of this home lies in its gourmet kitchen, featuring an 8-burner Wolf range a dream come true for culinary enthusiasts. The kitchen seamlessly integrates with the living spaces, providing an ideal environment for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet family moments. Additional features elevate this residence to a realm of opulence. A built-in generator guarantees continuous power supply, while a hidden temperature-controlled wine cellar awaits those with a penchant for fine vintages. For added security, discover a discreet safe room/panic room, offering peace of mind in every corner. Entertainment is effortlessly woven into the fabric of this property with a built-in speaker system throughout. Step outside to practice your golf put on your personal putting green, offering a touch of recreational luxury. The expansive .3-acre property provides plenty of space for future additions, including the potential for a private pool. The main floor features an owner's suite that embodies luxury living, complete with two large walk-in closets, outside access, and vaulted ceilings to allow natural light to flood the room. This residence is not just a home; it's a lifestyle a testament to comfort, security, and timeless elegance. Embrace the sense of community in this private enclave, adorned with stunning old oak trees, serene walking trails, a fountain pond to sit and reflect in peaceful serenity. Water enthusiasts will delight in the proximity to the neighborhood dock, offering easy access to the water to fish and the convenient Remley's landing to drop in your boat for a day of fishing or a sunset cruise on the Wando and Cooper Rivers.   Convenience meets luxury as this extraordinary residence is strategically located just 6 miles from the vibrant heart of downtown Charleston. Immerse yourself in the rich history and culinary delights of this charming city, with its array of amazing restaurants and cultural experiences awaiting your exploration. For those seeking a coastal escape, the property is also perfectly situated just over 6 miles from the pristine shores of Sullivan's Island. Bask in the sun, stroll along the beaches, and revel in the coastal lifestyle, all within a short distance from the tranquility of your elegant abode. This unparalleled combination of proximity to both urban and coastal attractions makes this residence not only a home of timeless luxury but also a gateway to the best that Charleston has to offer.  Schedule an exclusive private tour today and experience firsthand the unparalleled grandeur of this meticulously designed residence. Welcome to a life of refinement and opulence!
